reviewText: A forced buy for school.  Did the trick.  Basic info, nothing fancy.  Fast shipping.
Don't waste your money - you can find these videos on youtube.
Not real impressed with this video series.

Very clear and easy to follow along with! Easy to learn and practice health assessments right along with the videos. Complete health examination as well as focused assessments depending on your needs. Very well organized!
I guess I got what I expected.  I needed them for school.  Still haven't used them, but will update if/when I do!
